      <h2>ABOUT US</h2>
      <p>We are a group of community-taught Software Engineers who gathered together build an app that would help not only us, but you with daily tasks!
      <br>As developers there is a lot on our minds, whether it is with day to day life or something pertaining to our careers. This app is designed to help everyone with just 1 or 100 tasks a day. It helps you prioritize those daily tasks to that you don't always have to rely on your second brain to remember those things. Simply add or delete tasks along the way. Your profile stays with you ever step of the way so you never loose track of those daily tasks!</p>
